channel.title: The Moto's Project
channel.description:
My friend and I, Have been working on A new server, We have been working on it for about 1 week, It is made off pimpscape :p
Creadits: pimpscape (for the base) silabgazar (For the items in the shops)
Green = Done, yellow = half way, Red = not started
New home New shops New starting equipment Added silab's all new things in the shop's Full mining full smithing full wood cutting Removing all the commands (for a challange) adding more shops adding more skills fixing up that annoying mouth and beard bug
Adding more quest/mini's setting up 508 (still thinking about it)
Well here are the pictures :p [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img88.imageshack.us/img88/6682/serverpic1de5.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img88/serverpic1de5.png/1/][IMG]http://img88.imageshack.us/img88/serverpic1de5.png/1/w772.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img141.imageshack.us/img141/206/serverpic2ez7.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img141/serverpic2ez7.png/1/][IMG]http://img141.imageshack.us/img141/serverpic2ez7.png/1/w772.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img141.imageshack.us/img141/4648/serverpic2el3.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img141/serverpic2el3.png/1/][IMG]http://img141.imageshack.us/img141/serverpic2el3.png/1/w772.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img75.imageshack.us/img75/5755/serverpic3xn4.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img75/serverpic3xn4.png/1/][IMG]http://img75.imageshack.us/img75/serverpic3xn4.png/1/w772.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img75.imageshack.us/img75/412/serverpic4rv1.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img75/serverpic4rv1.png/1/][IMG]http://img75.imageshack.us/img75/serverpic4rv1.png/1/w774.png[/img][/URL]
